# AI Development Guidelines

## Project Overview

This is a Next.js 16 fashion app landing page project (clamby.id) - a company profile site using React 19, TypeScript, and Tailwind CSS 4. The project uses shadcn/ui components and follows strict architectural principles.

## Core Technologies

- **Framework**: Next.js 16 (App Router)
- **UI Library**: React 19
- **Language**: TypeScript (strict mode)
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS 4
- **Components**: shadcn/ui (New York style)
- **Icons**: Lucide React
- **Fonts**: Geist Sans & Geist Mono
- **Animation**: Motion (motion) - modern animation library

